data.description: Welcome to your dream lakefront home! Experience modern luxury in this well-maintained 3 bed, 3 bath, 1 car garage townhome, built in 2019, with Lennar's Everything's Included(r) package, including stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, wood-finish cabinetry, oversized ceramic tile flooring, and Wi-Fi CERTIFIED(tm) Home Design, featuring smart home technology by Amazon and the ring video doorbell pro. Enjoy resort-style amenities such as a clubhouse, swimming pool, fitness center, party room, outdoor tennis and basketball courts, and a kids' playground. Located minutes from I-95, Vero Beach Regional airport, beaches, restaurants, and shopping, including the Vero Beach Outlets. Indulge in complete peace of mind and embrace a life of comfort and style in this stunning townhome.
